---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Refund Policy — Aishit Dharwal" description="Refund Policy for AI Classroom cohorts and services offered by Aishit Dharwal / Kapaso Technologies LLP.">
  <div class="container">
    <section class="legal-hero">
      <a href="/" class="back-link">← aishitdharwal.me</a>
      <h1>Refund Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal-date">Last updated: November 26, 2025</p>
    </section>

    <div class="legal-body">

      <p>Thank you for choosing to learn with Aishit Dharwal and AI Classroom. This Refund Policy explains the terms that apply when you purchase access to any workshop, cohort or program offered by Kapaso Technologies LLP.</p>

      <h2>Refund Eligibility</h2>
      <p>A full refund is available when the request is made within 48 hours from the scheduled commencement date and time of the workshop or cohort. Refund requests made after the completion of this 48 hour window are not eligible for any kind of refund.</p>

      <h2>How to Request a Refund</h2>
      <p>To request a refund, you must send an email to <a href="mailto:contact@kapasotechnologies.com">contact@kapasotechnologies.com</a> with the following details:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your full name</li>
        <li>Your registered email used during purchase</li>
        <li>Your registered mobile number</li>
        <li>Proof of identity such as Aadhaar card</li>
        <li>Payment reference ID or a payment screenshot</li>
        <li>Reason for requesting the refund</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Your request will be reviewed and processed within 5–7 working days.</p>

      <h2>Situations Where Refunds Are Not Provided</h2>
      <p>Refunds will not be provided in the following situations:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>If the refund request is made after 48 hours from the scheduled commencement date and time</li>
        <li>If you have attended the workshop or cohort, even partially</li>
        <li>If you have accessed or downloaded workshop materials</li>
        <li>If the workshop link or materials have been shared with others</li>
      </ul>
      <p>These rules ensure fairness to all participants and prevent misuse of the workshop pricing structure.</p>

      <h2>Mode of Refund</h2>
      <p>If approved, refunds will be processed to the original mode of payment.</p>
      <div class="legal-callout">
        <p class="legal-bold">Important Note</p>
        <p>Payment gateway fees are not refundable. The cost of payment gateway transactions is solely borne by the purchaser of the workshop or program.</p>
      </div>

      <h2>Modification or Cancellation of the Workshop</h2>
      <p>You acknowledge that we are under no obligation to refund any fees and applicable charges paid by you, in full or partially, under any circumstances including modifying or extending the duration of the service, change in the commencement date of the service, your failure to attend or participate in the service, or modification of the structure or content of the service.</p>

      <h2>Acceptance of This Policy</h2>
      <p>By purchasing any workshop or program offered by Aishit Dharwal or Kapaso Technologies LLP, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Refund Policy and agree to follow it.</p>

      <div class="legal-agreement">
        You have read this Refund Policy and agree to all of the provisions contained above.
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
